headline: GoDaddy (GDDY) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of domain registrar and web services company GoDaddy (NYSE:GDDY) fell 3.2% in the afternoon session after UBS lowered its price target on the stock, citing concerns over competition from artificial intelligence.
